messageBody:
Just a quick note. In the past, we have occasionally had members
whose e-mail address began bouncing. So even though we have been over
300 members for awhile, when you took the bouncing members into
account, we were just keeping above the 300 mark.

Today, we have no bouncing members, and we are at 313! This is a new
high water mark for our membership.

Introduce your friends to QS -- See which ones don't think you're
crazy. :).

Paige
